### Overview

The **IoTextra Input** is part of the **IoTextra series**, a family of modular hardware designed to simplify automation and control system development.

Each input channel is fully isolated, allowing safe monitoring of higher-voltage digital signals while protecting the control electronics. This design makes the module suitable for interfacing sensors, switches, and industrial control signals.

The IoTextra series serves as a fundamental building block of the ecosystem built around the **Make Things Happy philosophy**, bridging the gap between **rapid prototyping** and **industrial-grade reliability**.

